{"tid":1973524,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"爾母逝矣","createTime":"2020-04-15T08:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T16:16:41.000Z","uid":123119,"like":78,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"638601b4363047bb29d19dab4286bda4af70e399","tid":1973524,"uid":123119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:44:17.000Z","msg":"夫吾國互訊者眾，猶以微信、微博爲首，皆爲國製，可抵外夷窳敗詆誣。至於夷人，訊法甚異，尤以<ins>咪夷</ins>製者眾。顏典、囀遞、鬨廷、脈通、曷使、穹訊、遙旨，儀異而效同。惟夷民可暢言，或蔑或貶，損吾國譽，故自<ins>共習帝</ins>踐祚，卽禁國民用之，以防外夷劣術隳吾眾志、擾吾民心、妨吾國計也。<br />\n<br />\n噫！惜乎今人終日挊電札、翫電笏，聞鄙樂、賞俗舞，智亡而辭窮矣。<ins>暹羅</ins>頃日有夫襃其細君猶<ins>鯤島</ins>佳人，吾眾遂大舉越墉詈之，惟氣量、辭術皆拙，未數言輒曰「<strong>爾母逝矣</strong>」，此非徒增笑乎？民智未益，受夷嘲啁乃咎由自取矣。"},{"pid":"ade3ac6c109e05d4b05d9129a694d66fceaff864","tid":1973524,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4d3798e6465cf674406e0dd8535018b21426bb2","tid":1973524,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"nmsl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a61b58bb1da5dd34335727d762deb93ecfa02f","tid":1973524,"uid":122134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:49:28.000Z","msg":"估唔到原來咁高文學修為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3f6be84bfdc7263ba1975c8465275d3732fec1","tid":1973524,"uid":322623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"我好多字唔識讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673914302f25477263dc25d2971198153fb234d2","tid":1973524,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"睇得明你篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但未讀過出處"},{"pid":"6626c5eb92925b4ac41331c0c5ba7fc9ed166a56","tid":1973524,"uid":8308,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedB