By":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"咪夷=Meme？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:19:10.000Z","msg":"係美國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:23:41.000Z","msg":"原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cff2258db71b3459d72a81edc9595ee810e4c9","tid":1973524,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"我國網民眾多，以微信、微博爲首，都是國產，可抵禦外國人詆毀誣衊(說三道四)。至於外國人，通訊軟件甚多，尤其是美國製造的。Facebook, twitter, ??, ??, ??, ??, ??, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除了外觀它們效用一樣。但外國人可以暢言，他們又侮蔑又貶抑，令我國國譽受損。所以自中共習帝登基後，隨即禁止國民使用這些軟體，以防止外國人用邪惡方法毀壞我國人民，擾亂民心，妨礙我國國計(大國掘起)。"},{"pid":"0c9190f532b04f5bccb3871df829c6bbab8b2764","tid":1973524,"uid":127905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:30:26.000Z","msg":"中國有很多通訊軟件, 最多人用微信、微博。微信、微博都是國產軟件，可以防止外國勢力抵毀、誣蔑。而外國的通訊方式不一樣，很多是美國整造，例子有&quot;顏典、囀遞、鬨廷、脈通、曷使、穹訊、遙旨&quot;。 在外國的通訊軟件,，可以歌頌政府，亦可以批評，更可以損害我國聲。故此，自習近平上任以來，立刻禁止(我國)國民使用，以防外國勢力妖言惑眾、挑撥離間，擾亂我國民心，妨礙<del>習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想</del>國家有效施政。<br />\n<br />\n寫住第一段先，果七個軟件遲下再譯，估緊"},{"pid":"ee8e093b142b061d7cc1dae8f7b746069d2080b1","tid":1973524,"uid":277649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:42:49.000Z","msg":"nmsl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74016b54bdb10cc72f46148a37b34eb07dc99ee6","tid":1973524,"uid":277649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51c37db79ca3477213751089dfc52dae9146b1b5","tid":1973524,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"005e1f7973868aae32317175cdcfb9f59dd73890","tid":1973524,"uid":127905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b50a25b9170a2edbbcbdb3e79bb7f3b50509027f","tid":1973524,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"咪夷=Meme？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:19:10.000Z","msg":"係美國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:23:41.000Z","msg":"原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"夷即係國嘛 同埋佢有專名號"},{"pid":"54c240640e48b943f97a38dacac638297bf152e8","tid":1973524,"uid":127905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"第二段<br />\n(嘆息) 觀乎現代人終日沉醉於玩手機，玩電腦、聽抖音(?)、觀賞低俗的直播/舞踏，以致其智力低下而詞窮。有一天一個秦國男人讚賞佢女友很有台灣女孩的風格(好似違返史實)，接着我國便大舉跨越國境出言反擊，可惜國人氣量差(小氣)，又詞窮。開口未到幾句便是NMSL，此舉難度不是更加讓人恥笑嗎? 民智水平不足，受外國嘲笑是咎由自取"},{"pid":"34091f333d9e13e0e36174eb59d88c1c73f301ba","tid":1973524,"uid":127905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:50:11.000Z","msg":"果七個軟件投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係知囀遞 = twitter"},{"pid":"1e3470f3e6908c6fca5a1a2f41854965501c7920","tid":1973524,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"肏汝娘乙乎？"},{"pid":"9cf77bf214d2357c1408bb94a184ed14aba93b9c","tid":1973524,"uid":123119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夫吾國互訊者眾，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">尤</span></strong>以微信、微博爲首，皆爲國製&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n而家先發現自己打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201318ed67c34e25b8f0a6f8299e884c8dc36c6e","tid":1973524,"uid":2526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"共習帝"},{"pid":"816441534e6cf5d5e620e6c4712a5107c3413272","tid":1973524,"uid":227062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"鬨廷=discord?<br />\n脈通=line?"},{"pid":"f248724685eefa9c76aee74148e8aeecde1d3ffb","tid":1973524,"uid":140000,"like":1,"dislike"